Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼·德普诉前妻 安柏·赫德的诽谤案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Welcome back. Johnny Depp's defamation trial
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在电视上和社交媒体上同步直播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is playing out in real time on television and on social media,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（2022年4月 弗吉尼亚）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有数以百万记的人 在爆出惊人的细节 并且站边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where millions are poring over shocking details and taking sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（抖音）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏 你感觉如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber, how you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我关于这集节目的视频 有将近50万播放量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My video about this pod episode is at almost 500,000 views,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而那期视频是我昨天才发布的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I just posted it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须看到很多方面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It has many facets that we have to look at,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括名声 “我也是”运动 取消文化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}including fame, the Me Too movement, cancel culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这简直就是一场完美风暴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is just a, uh... sort of a perfect storm, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超过埃隆·马斯克成为第一名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Number one over Elon Musk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是乔·拜登的四倍以上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}More than four times Joe Biden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是堕胎意见的五倍以上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Abortion opinion, more than five times greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是乌克兰战争的六倍以上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Ukraine war, more than six times greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:01:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是全国互联网上最热门的事件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This story is the biggest story online in the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（在审判期间 有超过200小时的实况报道）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（数以百万计的人 收看、评论和分享）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新闻主播在法院外排起了长队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}News anchors lined up outside the courthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法庭里有很多摄像头 每分钟都在直播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Numerous cameras inside the courtroom live-streaming every minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带我们去参观一下 可以给我们的移动设备拍个视频\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, take us for a little tour of our... I think we have video of our mobile setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里有时会有供暖和空调\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We actually have heating and air conditioning sometimes in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在推特直播 在视频直播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People are live-tweeting, people are live-streaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都是什么意思？最后如何收场？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What does it all mean? Where does it end?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这成为了社交媒体马戏团\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's been, uh, you know, a social media circus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充斥着来自 创作者、网红和普通人的评论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of commentary from creators and influencers and, uh... and laypeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这件事的真正意义 早就被社交媒体遗忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think that the truth was lost on social media, uh, quite some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家对抖音上 传播的错误信息有了新的担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, there are new concerns about the spread of misinformation on TikTok.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,研究人员调查显示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}According to researchers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国用户在抖音上 花费的时间比在推特上长三倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}American users spend three times as much time on TikTok than on Twitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多给我们解释一下 这个应用程序的设计和它的麻烦之处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Explain for us more about the app's design and why it is particularly problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个短视频平台\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have a platform that uses short videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它有一个非常强大而神秘的推荐算法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It has a powerful and very mysterious recommendation algorithm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:01:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它有十亿用户\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've got a billion users
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不断地快速筛选视频\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that are constantly filtering through a very fast-moving feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,视频可以很轻易地被操控和重新发布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Videos can be very easily manipulated and republished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走出卧室时 一巴掌打在我脸上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was walking out of the bedroom, slapped me across the face,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说：“约翰尼 你打我”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I said, "Johnny, you hit me."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You just hit me. Hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一些模仿视频会被很多人当真\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There are parody videos that often get mistaken as fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们当时并肩坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们都痴迷于这个案件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People are obsessed with this case. On TikTok,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们可以在抖音上广播他们的理论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}people could really broadcast their theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时坐在地毯上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was sitting there on this carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是这个案件被直播 你可以拿到全程录像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Especially when the case is live in court and you have all this footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以给他们看到真实发生的事情 大家在发什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You could show them authentically what is going on. What are people posting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聊聊澳大利亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...talked about Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这可能会决定这个案件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think this might decide the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是双方争论最激烈的矛盾焦点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because this is where the parties are alleging the most significant dispute,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他们的说法完全相反\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they're in such contradiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪审团只能认同其中一个的真实性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that the jury can only think one of them is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为他们会得出结论 其中一方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think they're going to come to the conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在澳大利亚的事情上撒了谎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that one of them is lying about Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来看看他们描述的事情经过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's take a look about what they said happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时在参与 《加勒比海盗5》的拍摄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was... I was working on Pirates of the Caribbean five.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生 当时赫德小姐 和你一起在澳大利亚吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Depp, was Ms. Heard in Australia with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她后来过来了 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She came a little later, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德小姐去澳大利亚 找你的时候 发生了什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what happened when Ms. Heard came to visit you in Australia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《德普 vs 赫德： 好莱坞夫妻诽谤案》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剧名：《第二集：全网关注》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 约翰尼·德普来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you very much. Johnny Depp's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说过这件事 现在终于看到了 你有一枚订婚戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I haven't seen it, but I know it ahead of time, and now I see it,that you're wea... wearing a, uh... a... you have an engagement ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（2014年4月 《大卫·莱特曼深夜秀》）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的 我戴了一枚女性订婚戒指 -对 但你要结婚了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I do, I have a female engagement ring... - Yeah. - ...on my finger. - But you... you, uh, uh, you're getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Well, it's... uh, yeah. Uh, yeah. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 但男人戴订婚戒指 这不是很常见 对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But it's... it's not typical for a m-man to wear an engagement ring, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不常见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的女孩戴嫌大了 所以…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was too big for my girl, so, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的结婚对象…对了 她也上过节目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So the woman you're, uh... Who's been on the show, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-安柏 是的 -很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Amber, yeah. Yeah. - Oh, lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏 向左看！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber, look to your left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏 笑一个 安柏！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber. Big smile, Amber!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我几年前就向赫德小姐求婚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had proposed to Ms. Heard a couple of years before, I believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们偶尔会聊一聊 什么时候适合抽出时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so we talked occasionally about when would be the right time between schedules
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来举办婚礼和度蜜月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so that we could actually have a wedding and a honeymoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后去澳大利亚工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and... and then go on to do the work in Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要和我的一生挚爱结婚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was marrying the love of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这很复杂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was complicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他曾是我的一生挚爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but he was the love of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士们 先生们 约翰尼·德普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen, Johnny Depp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We all left for the island for the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦想中的婚礼上岛的 大概吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}well, the dream wedding, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走过沙滩步道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We walked down the beach aisle, 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了我们的誓言 在祭坛上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}said our vows,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对狗仔队竖了中指\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and shot the bird, meaning the middle finger, up at the paparazzi while we were on the altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们跳舞和庆祝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we danced and celebrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我离开了岛屿 因为我得去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then I left the island 'cause I had to go work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏！请看前面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber! Straight ahead please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏·赫德比他年轻20岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber Heard is 20 years younger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在好莱坞建立了 自己的事业和知名度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and was building a career and name recognition within Hollywood,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她还远不是 约翰尼·德普那样的明星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but she was certainly nowhere near the star that Johnny Depp was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们跟安柏·赫德在一起 -你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hi, we're here with Amber Heard. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介绍一下你的角色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Explain quickly your character.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我扮演的是一个年轻女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I play a young girl who's caught up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（圣丹斯电影节 2009年）\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷入了洛杉矶1980年代 快节奏且贪图享乐的生活方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the fast-paced, decadent, 1980s lifestyle of Los Angeles,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是一个美丽的女人 最终…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's a beautiful woman who ultimately, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最终 这种美丽 导致了她和其他人物的灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ultimately, that beauty causes her demise and the demise of other characters around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个很有趣的角色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And it was an interesting part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在洛杉矶搭乘公交车 那是在智能手机时代之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I took the bus around L.A. It was before smartphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿着托马斯街道地图和换洗的背心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had a... a Thomas Guide and a change of tank tops,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常努力地跑试镜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I just hustled from one audition to the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这里 安柏 -安柏 这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Right here, Amber. - Amber, right here.
