Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.16,0:25:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邓布罗斯基小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Miss Dembrowski, 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.12,0:25:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和你双亲的关系如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}how would you describe your parents' relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.88,0:25:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很复杂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That was complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.84,0:25:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的童年…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, I had a very...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.84,0:25:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...interesting childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.08,0:25:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到一定年纪前 我都以为我的童年很普通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}um, one that I thought was normal until a certain age.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.24,0:25:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能告诉他们你吸毒的历史吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could you please tell them about your history of substance use?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.80,0:25:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概在四五岁的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}At about the age of, I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.48,0:25:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也说不好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}f-four, five years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.00,0:25:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚地记得我妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I... I can remember vividly my... my mom
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.44,0:25:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我从她挂在门后的包里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}telling me to go get her nerve pills, you know, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.16,0:25:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去拿她的神经药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}out of her purse that was hanging on the back of the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.32,0:25:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会去拿神经药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I'd go get the nerve pills and I'd take it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.56,0:25:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几年后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, um, you know, after a few years,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.36,0:25:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开始注意到…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you start to notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.80,0:25:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开始想“神经药”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}well, you start to think about "nerve pills."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.64,0:25:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“神经药”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Nerve pill."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.00,0:26:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她吃了那些“神经药”之后 似乎会平静下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then she seemed to calm down after she took those "nerve pills."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.32,0:26:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以当我11岁的时候…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, when I was 11 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.00,0:26:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想冷静下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanted to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.56,0:26:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮我妈妈拿她的神经药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd bring my mom her nerve pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.56,0:26:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会走开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I would walk away...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.32,0:26:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我自己也吃一颗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...and I would take one myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.48,0:26:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用来逃避我们当时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to escape the... the chaotic... nature
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.64,0:26:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常混乱的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of... of what w... of what we were living, uh, through.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.20,0:26:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My mother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.08,0:26:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常难以预测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}quite unpredictable,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.36,0:26:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且她非常暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she was quite violent,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.68,0:26:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有身体上的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the physical pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.36,0:26:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们学会应对 学会接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}y-you learn to deal with, you learn to accept it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.60,0:26:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但心理和情感上的虐待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the, uh, psychological and emotional abuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.32,0:27:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得会把我们撕成碎片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's what, uh...that's what kind of tore us up, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.24,0:27:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生 你有没有过药物上瘾？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Depp, is there any substance you've ever been addicted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.72,0:27:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有 -是什么药物？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yes. - And... And what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.16,0:27:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛西考酮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Roxicodone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.32,0:27:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止 大家都在用自己读到的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So far, everybody's just making these speculations
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.76,0:27:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行推测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}based off of whatever they're reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.56,0:27:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在此之前 都没有听过当事人的陈述\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We haven't heard it out of the horse's mouth until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.32,0:27:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们听到了 或者开始听到这些事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And now that we have, or started to hear about these things...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.04,0:27:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只会让他看起来 是一个更加真诚的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it only makes him seem like a more honest human being,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.92,0:27:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更加讨喜的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a more likable person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.48,0:27:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上瘾的药物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The pills that I was addicted to, the... 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.24,0:27:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛西考酮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the Roxicodone,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.92,0:27:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是非常强大的阿片类药物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which are very, very powerful opiates,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.12,0:27:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两颗就能让我失去意识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}two of those would knock me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.52,0:27:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会开始所谓的“点头”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You go on what's called "the nod,"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.88,0:27:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后它会让你立即沉睡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then it takes you away into sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.04,0:27:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是非常深的睡眠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just very deep sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.12,0:27:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到约翰尼·德普 对自己的药物滥用史非常坦诚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We see Johnny Depp very open about his drug use,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.72,0:27:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为另一方会试图用这一点扳倒他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that I think the other side was going to try to use against him,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.68,0:28:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他知道 他会承认 他的朋友也承认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but he knew, he's going to admit to it, his friends admitted to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.28,0:28:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们让对方的攻击不那么有杀伤力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they kind of, you know, took the sting out of it from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.84,0:28:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么严重后果了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They... Nothing really happened with it anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.24,0:28:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦你承认了 他们就做不了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Once you admit it, they can't really do anything with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.08,0:28:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法采取行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's no movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.08,0:28:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一张你在 黑色皮沙发上昏倒的照片 是么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is a picture of you on a... on a black leather couch, passed out, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.12,0:28:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昏倒是一种有趣的说法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Passed out's an interesting way of putting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.28,0:28:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是睡着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe "asleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.68,0:28:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大腿上的是冰淇淋 对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's ice cream on your lap, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.28,0:28:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is indeed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.36,0:28:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德小姐让我拿着冰淇淋 因为她注意到我在点头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, Ms. Heard asked me to hold the ice cream as she noticed that I was on a... on the nod,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.28,0:28:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是快睡着了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that means "falling asleep,"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.20,0:28:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那天工作了17个小时 而且我摄入了阿片类药物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}um, from the 17-hour day that I'd worked, and also the opiates that I'd ingested,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.04,0:28:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是她拍的一张绝妙的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and that was a wonderful picture to take for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.56,0:28:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道她为什么要拍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Sure... - I don't know why she took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.00,0:28:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以拍到那张照片是赫德小姐的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, so it's Ms. Heard's fault that that picture was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.80,0:28:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这意思吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's... Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.96,0:28:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她拍的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She... She snapped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.56,0:28:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪审团对这个信息的解读会很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Interesting to see how the jury interpret this information.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.52,0:28:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会像赫德希望的那样 认为是约翰尼拥有黑暗面的证据？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will they interpret it, as Ms. Heard wants, as evidence of Johnny having a "dark side"?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.44,0:29:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是说他们会像约翰尼说的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will they interpret it as evidence, as Johnny says,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.80,0:29:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解读成女朋友 故意让她的伴侣看起来像坏人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of a girlfriend setting up her partner to look like a bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.92,0:29:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关注我 了解更多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Follow me for more legal TikTok.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.28,0:29:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你拍了这张照片吗 赫德小姐？ -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You took this photo, right, Ms. Heard? - That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.96,0:29:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你决定拍德普睡在地板上的照片？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you decided to take a picture of Mr. Depp asleep on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.40,0:29:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他昏倒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.68,0:29:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也拍了这张照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You took this picture as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.80,0:29:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.08,0:29:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是德普先生度假时 在他的热带岛屿上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is a picture of Mr. Depp taking a nap on his tropical island, on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.40,0:29:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小憩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.36,0:29:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在度假 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We were on vacation, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.88,0:29:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你也拍了这张照片吗 赫德小姐？ -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You also took this picture, right, Ms. Heard? - That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.88,0:29:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是德普先生 睡在椅子上的另一张照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And this is another picture of Mr. Depp asleep in a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.00,0:29:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他在点头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, he was, um, nodding off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.88,0:29:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, "asleep" is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.60,0:29:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你在点头时 说明你嗑药嗑嗨了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When you're nodding off, you're high on drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.56,0:29:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他甚至没有感觉到 拿在手上的香烟烧到了他的腿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't even feel the cigarette in his hand that had, you know, been burning on his leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.52,0:29:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这是警报 因为我非常在意他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, it was cause for alarm for me, naturally, um, because I cared about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.28,0:29:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎很喜欢 在德普先生睡觉的时候给他拍照\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You seem to like taking pictures of Mr. Depp while he's sleeping, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.52,0:29:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常讨厌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.00,0:29:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你决定拍一张德普 浑身都是冰淇淋睡着的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You decided to take a picture of Mr. Depp asleep with ice cream spilled all over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.44,0:30:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这照片里的他不是很好看吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This isn't a very flattering picture of Mr. Depp, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.96,0:30:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.88,0:30:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把这张照片发给了你的朋友 洛基佩宁顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You did, in fact, send this picture to your friend, Rocky Pennington.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.68,0:30:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我发了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.60,0:30:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你在保护德普先生吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And this is you protecting Mr. Depp?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.80,0:30:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我在寻求最好朋友的支持\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is me getting support from my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.04,0:30:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你在支持德普先生吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is you supporting Mr. Depp?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.84,0:30:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我寻求最好朋友的支持\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is me getting support from my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.28,0:30:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也需要支持\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I also need support.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.68,0:30:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- My God, I'm... - I'm so disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.60,0:30:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对你很失望 安迪 这太让人难过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm so disappointed in you, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.76,0:30:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 各位 真相已经出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm so sorry, guys. The truth is there. It's so upsetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.04,0:30:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是怪物 因为我昨晚在床上昏倒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm a monster. I must be a monster because I passed out on my bed last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.32,0:30:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚米拍了一张照片 然后就完了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Yami took a photo and it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.76,0:30:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们敢相信吗 这都能被作为证据？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you guys friggin' believe this was put into evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.32,0:30:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在度假的时候小憩了一下 这照片是他妈什么东西？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's taking a freaking nap on vacation! Like, what the fuck is this photo?
