Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.20,0:42:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,匹诺曹可能要告她盗窃身份 因为她撒了这么多谎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pinocchio might have to sue her for identity theft, these lies are getting out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.84,0:42:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你捐钱直接认捐就可以了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You pay donations through pledging them?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.28,0:42:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你得付钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, you pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.00,0:42:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你捐钱是把钱给他们 而不是说你会给他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You give donations by giving them money,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.60,0:42:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not by saying you're going to give them money.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.72,0:42:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不知道捐赠和认捐的区别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She doesn't know the difference between "donate" and "pledge."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.56,0:42:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.68,0:42:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我会“安柏·赫德”这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think I'm gonna "Amber Heard" it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.08,0:42:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认捐1000或1200万美元给大组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pledge ten, twelve million dollars to a great organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.44,0:42:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然认捐和捐赠是同义词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, and since "pledge" and "donate" is synonymous,
