Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.32,0:44:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想的是“这一定是…” 我猜想陪审团已经被隔离了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was thinking about that too. Like, "This has gotta be..." I mean, like, I'm assuming the jury's, like, sequestered away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.96,0:44:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-对 -这是个很大的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - This is a big...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.08,0:44:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟什么东西隔离开？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sequestered away from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.68,0:44:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲利普 你觉得社交媒体有多重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Philip, let me start with you. How important do you think social media is, and what's going on out there
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.28,0:44:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在社交媒体领域 对这个案件有什么看法？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the social media universe, to this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.60,0:44:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正重要的是 你有一个由七个人组成的陪审团\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All that really matters is that you have a jury of seven
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.64,0:44:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会在社交媒体上发表言论 他们会纯粹根据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who does not go on social media and is going to assess what went down based purely on 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.60,0:44:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法庭上提出的内容 而不是抖音或照片墙帖子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what is presented in court and not what is, you know, on TikTok or in Instagram posts
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.28,0:44:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或脸书上的内容等等 来评估发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or on Facebook, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.44,0:44:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（米歇尔·托马斯 辩护律师 法庭卫视音频）\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.72,0:44:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可以跟亲朋好友互动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They've been able to interact with friends, family,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.52,0:44:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们不应该参与社交媒体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and so, while they're not supposed to engage in social media
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.36,0:44:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不应知道公共领域发生了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and know what's going on in the public sphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.64,0:44:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很难说陪审团里没有人接触过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's kind of tough to say that no one on that jury has been exposed to it whatsoever,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.96,0:44:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的确认为那是个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so I do think that's a concern.
