Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.60,0:44:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有那间法庭里的人群\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the impact of the crowd cannot be overlooked
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.24,0:44:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是不能被忽视的影响因素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in that courtroom every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.48,0:44:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得大多数情况下 陪审团都会做出正确判断吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you think that the jury gets it right in most cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.20,0:44:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得他们了解自己的责任吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you think that they understand their responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.32,0:44:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 法官会告知他们应该做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course, the judge tells them what they're supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.12,0:44:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能读关于这个案件的任何东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not to read anything about this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.80,0:45:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能看关于这个案件的任何东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are not to watch anything about this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.32,0:45:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能听关于这个案件的任何东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not to listen to anything about this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.64,0:45:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这适用于电视 报纸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This applies to television, newspapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.84,0:45:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杂志 网络 任何网站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}magazines, the Internet, and any online sites.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.04,0:45:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更进一步说 你不能读、看或听 任何与之相关的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Further, you're not to read, watch, or listen to anything about this case
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.08,0:45:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在任何社交网站上发布的内容 比如推特 脸书 照片墙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}on any social networking sites such as Twitter, Facebook, Instagram,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.84,0:45:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snapchat之类的 任何类似的网站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snapchat, etc., or any similar sites.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.76,0:45:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪审团应该被隔离起来 人们会希望他们不会查看任何东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The jury should've been sequestered. You would hope that they would not look up anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.80,0:45:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做陪审员很难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's very, very hard to be a juror.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.76,0:45:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不羡慕这些陪审员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I do not envy these jurors at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.52,0:45:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在法庭上待了六个星期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Six weeks being in that courtroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.12,0:45:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次 不好玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Again, it is not fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.52,0:45:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有一个人知道 自己会参与德普案的庭审\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not one of them had a fucking clue that they were walking into Johnny Depp's fucking trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.68,0:45:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得被转播是非常棒的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I-I think this is fantastic that this is being broadcasted,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.96,0:45:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我觉得一切都清晰起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I think that everything that's coming together,
